      <h2 id="when-to-claim" class="govuk-!-padding-top-6 govuk-heading-m">
        When to claim
      </h2>

      <p class="govuk-body">You can claim funding if you have set up a Get funding to improve animal health and welfare &#40IAHW&#41 agreement before the vet visit. The vet will give you a summary of the animal health and welfare review or endemic disease follow-up.</p>

      <p class="govuk-body">The service ends on 19 June 2027. Your review and follow-up visits must be done by then. You must submit your claims by 19 September 2027.</p>

      <p class="govuk-body">Your review claim must be approved before you claim for the resulting follow-up. You must have followed the guidance on <a href="#">planning reviews</a> and <a href="#">planning follow-ups</a>.</p>

